  "detailed_description": "<i>This is a game where you can survive, fight zombies and bandits and do all this together with a friend! The game has different weather conditions, including thunderstorms. You can move around in cars (just watch out for the mines left by your friend!)</i><br><br><strong>There are a lot of things you can do in this game, like just sit by the fire and have a heart-to-heart talk with a friend:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/5a2d660c82a3050ee8adbc55356a9e05.poster.avif?t=1729793155\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/5a2d660c82a3050ee8adbc55356a9e05.webm?t=1729793155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/5a2d660c82a3050ee8adbc55356a9e05.mp4?t=1729793155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>You can drive cars, race, and just travel around in them:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/c65884dbf49aae6883ef02c56767251b.poster.avif?t=1729793155\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/c65884dbf49aae6883ef02c56767251b.webm?t=1729793155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/c65884dbf49aae6883ef02c56767251b.mp4?t=1729793155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Kill bloodthirsty zombies and bandits, for protection of course)</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/d76e649a44b7d0c8d737f7f23298e88f.poster.avif?t=1729793155\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/d76e649a44b7d0c8d737f7f23298e88f.webm?t=1729793155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/d76e649a44b7d0c8d737f7f23298e88f.mp4?t=1729793155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The game is very funny, for example, a friend pointed a gun at me head:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/b059b970b38d2940726d3ebe40bc18da.poster.avif?t=1729793155\" width=540 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/b059b970b38d2940726d3ebe40bc18da.webm?t=1729793155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/b059b970b38d2940726d3ebe40bc18da.mp4?t=1729793155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>You can also hack various doors and chests!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/ef82125602fd81b13be551e93d82344e.poster.avif?t=1729793155\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/ef82125602fd81b13be551e93d82344e.webm?t=1729793155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/ef82125602fd81b13be551e93d82344e.mp4?t=1729793155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Farm to avoid starving to death:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/8eb4a682abd6af8f73f9d73ed7555833.poster.avif?t=1729793155\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/8eb4a682abd6af8f73f9d73ed7555833.webm?t=1729793155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/8eb4a682abd6af8f73f9d73ed7555833.mp4?t=1729793155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>This survival game is full of emotions and events, you will definitely not get bored in it! This demo does not have some features, but we think without them you will be able to appreciate all the advantages of this game!</i>",
  "about_the_game": "<i>This is a game where you can survive, fight zombies and bandits and do all this together with a friend! The game has different weather conditions, including thunderstorms. You can move around in cars (just watch out for the mines left by your friend!)</i><br><br><strong>There are a lot of things you can do in this game, like just sit by the fire and have a heart-to-heart talk with a friend:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/5a2d660c82a3050ee8adbc55356a9e05.poster.avif?t=1729793155\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/5a2d660c82a3050ee8adbc55356a9e05.webm?t=1729793155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/5a2d660c82a3050ee8adbc55356a9e05.mp4?t=1729793155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>You can drive cars, race, and just travel around in them:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/c65884dbf49aae6883ef02c56767251b.poster.avif?t=1729793155\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/c65884dbf49aae6883ef02c56767251b.webm?t=1729793155\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839350/extras/c65884dbf49aae6883ef02c56767251b.mp4?t=1729793155\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Kill bloodthirsty zombies and bandits, for protection of course)</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_